OL,3,CMan who led an 'angry' group before
OL,4,Ckicking two police officers jailed
OL,6,FFootage captured Roger Haywood leading
OL,7,Fthe mob and shouting to the crowd.
OL,9,FA man who led an "angry" group through
OL,10,Fa seaside town before kicking two
OL,11,Fpolice officers has been jailed.
OL,13,FRoger Haywood, 41, "actively
OL,14,Fencouraged others to use violence" as
OL,15,Fhe took the crowd through Blackpool,
OL,16,Fstopping at the Cenotaph, the Tower
OL,17,Fand the comedy carpet, the court heard.
