OL,3,CMan who led an 'angry' group before
OL,4,Ckicking two police officers jailed
OL,6,FEven when he was arrested Haywood
OL,7,Fcontinued to persuade others, shouting
OL,8,F"cause f*****g mayhem tonight" as he
OL,9,Fwas placed into the back of a police
OL,10,Fvan, in 3 August.
OL,12,FJailing him for two-and-a-half-years
OL,13,Fat Preston Crown Court, Judge Robert
OL,14,FAltham, said many had respectfully
OL,15,Fpaid tribute to Bebe King, six, Elsie
OL,16,FDot Stancombe, seven, and Alice de
OL,17,FSilva Aguiar.
