OL,4,Ckicking two police officers jailed
OL,6,FHaywood repeatedly verbally abused
OL,7,Fpolice officers, at one point
OL,8,Fcontinuing to approach a police line,
OL,9,F"jabbing a finger at them" and
OL,10,Frefusing to move away.
OL,12,FHe was "clearly in the lead" of a
OL,13,Flarge group of rioters, the judge
OL,14,Fsaid, leading them down the promenade,
OL,15,Fsome with flags and others with their
OL,16,Ffaces covered.
