OL,3,CMan who led an 'angry' group before
OL,4,Ckicking two police officers jailed
OL,6,FHe then took "the mob you led" into
OL,7,Fthe confined space of the Hounds Hill
OL,8,Fshopping centre, where "brave security
OL,9,Fstaff" who were "vastly outnumbered"
OL,10,Ftried to accompany them.
OL,12,FHaywood then attempted to pull up the
OL,13,Fshutters of JD Sports before he
OL,14,Fassaulted a member of its security
OL,15,Fteam, Lancashire Police said, others
OL,16,Fthen took over the attack.
