OL,3,CMan who led an 'angry' group before
OL,4,Ckicking two police officers jailed
OL,6,FLater, at the cenotaph, Haywood
OL,7,Fconfronted a line of police, where he
OL,8,Fagain encourage those in the mob
OL,9,Fbehind him to move forward towards the
OL,10,Fofficers.
OL,12,F"Your aim was clear, you wanted to
OL,13,Fcreate a serious, violent and
OL,14,Fdangerous incident," Judge Altham said.
OL,16,FHe was arrested on the same evening
OL,17,Fand assaulted an officer as they
OL,18,Fattempted to restrain him, kicking two
OL,19,Fofficers to the hand and arm.
