OL,3,CMan who led an 'angry' group before
OL,4,Ckicking two police officers jailed
OL,6,FHaywood pleaded guilty to two counts
OL,7,Fof assaulting an emergency worker and
OL,8,Fviolent disorder during unrest in
OL,9,FBlackpool when he appeared in court.
OL,11,FHaywood, of Yew Tree Close, pleaded
OL,12,Fguilty to violent disorder and assault
OL,13,Fand was jailed for 20 months.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
