OL,3,CMan who led an 'angry' group before
OL,4,Ckicking two police officers jailed
OL,6,FSarah Gallagher, District Crown
OL,7,FProsecutor for CPS Northwest, said:
OL,8,F"When a violent mob descended on
OL,9,FBlackpool on August 3, Roger Haywood
OL,10,Ftook a leading role in the disorder,
OL,11,Fencouraging others and behaving
OL,12,Faggressively towards members of the
OL,13,Fpublic and police officers.
OL,15,F"This vile behaviour cannot go
OL,16,Funchallenged. Those taking to the
OL,17,Fstreets, taking part in violent
OL,18,Fconduct and spreading fear in our
OL,19,Fcommunities must face the consequences
OL,20,Fof their actions."
