OL,3,CMan who led an 'angry' group before
OL,4,Ckicking two police officers jailed
OL,6,FAssistant Chief Constable Phil Davies,
OL,7,Fof Lancashire Police, said: "Haywood
OL,8,Fnot only chose to be violent himself,
OL,9,Fbut he actively encouraged others to
OL,10,Fuse violence too, and I welcome the
OL,11,Fcustodial sentence handed down on him.
OL,13,F"This sentencing shows just how
OL,14,Fseriously violent disorder is being
OL,15,Ftaken in our county. It will never be
OL,16,Ftolerated or taken lightly, and this
OL,17,Fsentencing is the first of many that
OL,18,Fwe will expect to see over the coming
OL,19,Fweeks and months."
